&uuml;&ccedil;in &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;N&auml;saglary&#328; 80-85% -de pankreatiti&#328;
&yacute;um&#351;ak agyrlygy bellen&yacute;&auml;r, hassalary&#328; takmynan 20%
-de agyr kursy&#328; alamatlary bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;So&#328;ky &yacute;yllarda
senagat ta&yacute;dan &ouml;sen &yacute;urtlarda &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;an keseller birn&auml;&ccedil;e gezek k&ouml;peldi, bu bolsa
&yacute;iti pankreatiti&#328; “siwilizasi&yacute;a keseli” h&ouml;km&uuml;nde
kesgitlenmegine m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

