</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Garyn agyry&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>birden, k&ouml;plen&ccedil;
ag&#351;am &yacute;a-da gije, i&yacute;mit s&auml;wliklerinden (alkogol,
gowrulan &yacute;a-da &yacute;agly i&yacute;mitler) &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;D&uuml;zg&uuml;n bol&#351;y &yacute;aly, gaty
g&uuml;&yacute;&ccedil;li, garny&#328; ortasynda &yacute;a-da &ccedil;ep
b&ouml;leginde g&ouml;wresi&#328; &uuml;st&uuml;nde
lokalla&#351;dyryl&yacute;ar, gapyrgalary&#328; a&#351;aky gyrasy, a&#351;aky
arkasy we egninde &yacute;a&yacute;rap
bil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;K&ouml;plen&ccedil; gu&#351;ak h&auml;si&yacute;etine
e&yacute;e bolup, gysyl&yacute;an gu&#351;ak du&yacute;gusyny
d&ouml;red&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
