color:black'>Gusmak&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>hemi&#351;e di&yacute;en
&yacute;aly agyry bilen bir wagtda &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;I&yacute;mit &yacute;a-da suw kabul etmek bilen
k&ouml;p bol&yacute;ar we &yacute;e&#328;illik getirme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
