</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Bedeni&#328; gyzgynlygyny&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>- k&ouml;plen&ccedil; subfribil sanlara;&nbsp;38-39 derejeden
&yacute;okary gyzzyrma uly zeper &yacute;etmegini &yacute;a-da
&yacute;oka&#351;magy g&ouml;rkezip biler.&nbsp;Keseli&#328; ikinji hepdesinden
ba&#351;lap, n&auml;saglarda&nbsp;<b>rezorptiw gyzzyrma&nbsp;</b>- a&#351;gazan
asty m&auml;zini&#328; zeperlenen &yacute;erlerinde
&ccedil;i&#351;m&auml;ni&#328; &ouml;smegi bilen baglany&#351;ykly
temperaturany&#328; &yacute;okarlanmagy bolup biler.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
