<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bar&#351;ynda&nbsp;<b>muayene,&nbsp;</b>lukman,
garyn &#350;efkat lokalizasyonu tespit garyn edaralaryny&#328; d&uuml;rli
keselleri tertibi alamatlary g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Laboratori&yacute;a barlagy</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&nbsp;<b>umumy gan barlag&nbsp;</b>, l&ouml;kositlerin sanynda
bir arty&#351; tespit &uuml;&ccedil;in ni&yacute;etlenen, agyr pankreatit-nji
&yacute;ylda, hemoglobin we trombositler derejede bir azalma k&auml;wagt
bar.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&nbsp;<b>biyokimyasal i&#351;&nbsp;</b>pankreas enzimlerin (artan
mazmunyny &yacute;&uuml;ze&nbsp;<b>amilaz&nbsp;</b>we&nbsp;<b>lipaz&nbsp;</b>)&nbsp;k&auml;n&nbsp;(bir
arty&#351; metabolik bozukluk bellikleri&nbsp;<b>gant&nbsp;</b>derejede&nbsp;,
bir azalma&nbsp;<b>protein&nbsp;</b>konsantrasyon&nbsp;, i&#351; elementlerin
we mineral d&uuml;z&uuml;minde
&uuml;&yacute;tge&#351;meler).&nbsp;Ectokan&ccedil;
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymlylyklary&#328; agyrlygyna baha bermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>C-reaktiw belok&nbsp;</b>we&nbsp;<b>prokalsitonin&nbsp;</b>&yacute;aly
g&ouml;rkezijiler&nbsp;ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bu organlary&#328; bozulmagyny
&yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;ykarmak&nbsp;&uuml;&ccedil;in bagyr i&#351;ini&#328;
g&ouml;rkezijileri (&nbsp;<b>bilirubin, ALT, AST&nbsp;</b>) we b&ouml;wrek
(&nbsp;<b>kreatini&#328;, karbamid&nbsp;</b>)
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Funksi&yacute;a,
radiasi&yacute;a we instrumental diagnostika</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Ultrases
barlagy&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328;
&yacute;a&yacute;ramagyna, &yacute;akyn organlary&#328; gatna&#351;magyna baha
berm&auml;ge, garyn bo&#351;lugynda suwuklygy&#328; bardygyny &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;ykarmaga m&uuml;mkin&ccedil;ilik ber&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Ultrases birn&auml;&ccedil;e
gezek ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r: keseli&#328; dinamikasyna baha bermek we
kyn&ccedil;ylyklary wagtynda kesgitlemek.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Adat&ccedil;a, pankreatiti&#328;
ilkinji diagnozy &uuml;&ccedil;in biohimiki gan synaglary we ultrases barlagy
&yacute;eterlikdir, &yacute;&ouml;ne kyn &yacute;agda&yacute;larda
go&#351;ma&ccedil;a&nbsp;<b>hasaplanan we magnit-rezonans
tomografi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</b>ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;.&nbsp;Hasaplanan
tomografi&yacute;a keseli&#328; 4-14-nji g&uuml;n&uuml;nde hem a&#351;gazan
asty m&auml;zine &yacute;etirilen zy&yacute;any&#328; agyrlygyna baha bermek we
so&#328;ra &yacute;&uuml;ze &ccedil;yk&yacute;an kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328;
&ouml;s&uuml;&#351;ine g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in
&yacute;erine &yacute;etiril&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Diagnostiki
laparoskopi&yacute;a&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, &yacute;agtylyk
&ccedil;e&#351;mesi we kameraly turbalary&#328; garny&#328; i&ccedil;ine
in&ccedil;e derini&#328; de&#351;ilmegi arkaly go&yacute;ul&yacute;an
amaldyr.&nbsp;Bu operasi&yacute;a bilen hirurglar garyn organlaryny barlap
bilerler we zerur bolsa lukman&ccedil;ylyk manipul&yacute;asi&yacute;alaryny
ge&ccedil;irip bilerler.&nbsp;Kesel anykla&yacute;y&#351; maksatlary
&uuml;&ccedil;in “Laparoskopi&yacute;a”, adat&ccedil;a, ultrases barlagyny&#328;
netijeleri &uuml;&ccedil;in, &#351;e&yacute;le hem be&yacute;leki &yacute;iti
garyn kesellerini &yacute;ok etmek &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;t haltasyny&#328;
(derini&#328; sarylygy) bozulmagyny&#328; alamatlary bar bolsa&nbsp;, &ouml;t
&yacute;oluny&#328; &ccedil;yk&yacute;an &yacute;agda&yacute;yna baha bermek
&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>fibrogastroduodenoskopi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>etmeli.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Bejergi
maksatlary</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Alamatlary &yacute;ok
etmek, a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; bitewiligini i&#328; &yacute;okary
derejede saklamak, &yacute;okan&ccedil; kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328;
&ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni almak we bejermek.&nbsp;Gaty pankreatitde - be&yacute;leki
organlary&#328; zeperlenmelerini go&#351;ma&ccedil;a intensiw bejermek,
bedeni&#328; m&ouml;h&uuml;m funksi&yacute;alaryna g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;ilik etmek
we goldamak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;
&yacute;oly we gurallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Yacute;iti pankreatitde&nbsp;azyndan
5 g&uuml;n&uuml;&#328; dowamynda&nbsp;<b>a&ccedil;lykdan&nbsp;</b>maslahat
beril&yacute;&auml;n a&#351;gazan asty ferment &#351;iresini&#328;
gyjyndyrylmagyny bes etmek&nbsp;.&nbsp;Pankreatitli n&auml;saglary&nbsp;<b>d&uuml;&#351;ekde
dyn&ccedil; almak &uuml;&ccedil;in bellemeli&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Dermanlar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Suwu&#328; we mineral maddalary&#328;
aly&#351;-&ccedil;al&#351;yny&#328; bozulmagyna, &#351;e&yacute;le hem serho&#351;lyga
-&nbsp;<b>erginleri&#328; damar infuzi&yacute;asyna&nbsp;</b>gar&#351;y
g&ouml;re&#351;i&#328;&nbsp;.&nbsp;Munu&#328; bilen birlikde diuretikler hem
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Bejergini&#328; bu usulyna &quot;mejbury diurez&quot;
di&yacute;il&yacute;&auml;r, z&auml;herli &ouml;n&uuml;mleri bedenden
&ccedil;alt a&yacute;yrmaga k&ouml;mek ed&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Agyry&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&yacute;yrmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in agyryny&nbsp;<b>a&yacute;yryjy&nbsp;</b>we&nbsp;<b>antispazmodikler&nbsp;</b>ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Pankreatiti&#328;
agyrylary gaty agyr bolup bil&yacute;&auml;ndigi seb&auml;pli, bu dermanlar ony
&yacute;e&#328;letmek &uuml;&ccedil;in elmydama &yacute;eterlik bolman
biler.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le &yacute;agda&yacute;larda&nbsp;<b>epidural
blokada&nbsp;</b>ulanyl&yacute;ar&nbsp;- o&#328;urga bilen o&#328;urga
&yacute;iligini&#328; arasyndaky bo&#351;luga anesteziki
giri&#351;.&nbsp;Epidural blok bilen di&#328;e anestezikany&#328;
sanjyl&yacute;an &yacute;erini&#328; a&#351;agyndaky agyry du&yacute;gurlygy
&yacute;ok bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Rus lukman&ccedil;ylyk tejribesinde a&#351;gazan astyndaky
fermentleri&#328; &ouml;n&uuml;m&ccedil;iligini basyp &yacute;atyrmak
&uuml;&ccedil;in oktreotid seri&#351;desi ulanyl&yacute;ar, &yacute;&ouml;ne
Amerikany&#328; we Europeanewropany&#328; tekliplerini&#328;
k&ouml;p&uuml;sinde, netijeliligini subut etme&yacute;&auml;nligi seb&auml;pli,
ulanmak maslahat berilme&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Belok &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi bolan n&auml;saglara&nbsp;<b>t&auml;ze
do&#328;durylan plazma &yacute;a-da albumin
ta&yacute;&yacute;arlanylmagyny&nbsp;</b>talap edip bilerler&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Antibakterial dermanlar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>di&#328;e
a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; nekrozyny&#328; (nekrozy&#328;
&yacute;erleri) &ouml;smegi &yacute;a-da &yacute;okan&ccedil;
kyn&ccedil;ylyklar bilen bellenil&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Zerur bolsa, &yacute;okumly maddalary&#328; damar bilen
dolandyrylmagy -&nbsp;<b>ene-atany&#328; i&yacute;mitlenmegi&nbsp;</b>bellenil&yacute;&auml;r&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gurmaklyk&nbsp;<b>gastrik t&uuml;p&nbsp;</b>(in&ccedil;e t&uuml;p)
we &uuml;sti bilen mide we duodenum mazmunyny a&yacute;yrmak (a&ccedil;lykdan
bellenen &yacute;aly &#351;ol bir maksat &uuml;&ccedil;in) a&#351;gazan
funksional galan d&ouml;retmek &uuml;&ccedil;in.&nbsp;Operasi&yacute;a otagynda
hirurg barlagy in&ccedil;e i&ccedil;eg&auml;ni&#328; derejesine go&yacute;up
biler, so&#328; bolsa a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; irki
d&ouml;wr&uuml;nde i&yacute;mitlenmek &uuml;&ccedil;in ulanylyp bilner,
seb&auml;bi bu &yacute;agda&yacute;da i&yacute;mit a&#351;gazan asty
m&auml;zini gyjyndyrmaz.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Gaty pankreatit bilen,&nbsp;<b>gany arassalamak&nbsp;</b>&uuml;&ccedil;in&nbsp;<b>ekstrakorporal&nbsp;</b>(&yacute;agny
adam bedenini&#328; da&#351;ynda)&nbsp;di&yacute;il&yacute;&auml;n&nbsp;<b>usullara&nbsp;</b>-
plazmaferez &yacute;a-da gemofiltrasi&yacute;a zerur bolup biler.&nbsp;</span><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Bu amallar wagtynda z&auml;herli birle&#351;meler
&yacute;&ouml;rite s&uuml;zg&uuml;&ccedil; enjamlary arkaly gandan
a&yacute;ryl&yacute;ar we arassalanan gan gana
ga&yacute;taryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Hirurgiki
amallar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Pankreatit bejergisinde
minimal invaziv tehnologi&yacute;alar (laparoskopi&yacute;a, ultrases
barlagynda perkutan drena)) we adaty a&ccedil;yk operasi&yacute;a
ulanyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Hirurgiki bejergini&#328; taktikasyny sa&yacute;lamak
&yacute;okan&ccedil; kyn&ccedil;ylyklary&#328;, garyn bo&#351;lugynda
&yacute;oka&#351;ma alamatlaryny&#328; we keseli&#328; be&yacute;leki
a&yacute;ratynlyklaryna baglydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ze&yacute;ke&#351; i&#351;leri&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>.&nbsp;Pankreatit
bilen, garyn bo&#351;lugynda a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; &#351;iresi,
gan we &ccedil;i&#351;me akymlary (eksudat) bar bolan suwuklyk &yacute;ygnanyp
biler.&nbsp;Ony a&yacute;yrmak &uuml;&ccedil;in minimal invaziv amallar
ulanyl&yacute;ar -&nbsp;<b>ultrases barlagynda&nbsp;laparoskopi&yacute;a&nbsp;</b>&yacute;a-da&nbsp;<b>ze&yacute;ke&#351;&nbsp;</b>.&nbsp;&#350;ol
bir wagty&#328; &ouml;z&uuml;nde, kamerany&#328; &yacute;a-da ultrases ses
dat&ccedil;igini&#328; g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iligi astynda derini&#328; de&#351;ilmegi
arkaly suwuklygy&#328; &yacute;ygnan&yacute;an &yacute;erine - &yacute;ygnanan
suwuklygy&#328; &ccedil;yk&yacute;an drenajyna in&ccedil;e turba
oturdyl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Ze&yacute;ke&#351;ler garyn operasi&yacute;alaryndan
so&#328;, meselem, pankreatiti&#328; &yacute;okan&ccedil; kyn&ccedil;ylyklary
&uuml;&ccedil;in gurul&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; operasi&yacute;asy&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>.&nbsp;A&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zinde nekrozy&#328; &ouml;smegi
bilen &ouml;len &yacute;erleri &yacute;a-da bezi&#328; bir b&ouml;legini
hirurgiki usulda a&yacute;yrmak amala a&#351;yryl&yacute;ar.&nbsp;Garyn
bo&#351;lugy nekrotik dokumalardan doly arassalan&yacute;an&ccedil;a &#351;e&yacute;le
amallary&#328; birn&auml;&ccedil;esi zerur bolup biler.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ectokan&ccedil; kyn&ccedil;ylyklar &uuml;&ccedil;in amallar&nbsp;</span></b><span
lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>.&nbsp;D&uuml;w&uuml;rtikleri&#328; we kistalary&#328; (suwuklyk
bilen doldurylan bo&#351;luklar) emele gelmegi bilen a&#351;gazan asty
m&auml;zini&#328; &ccedil;i&#351;megine k&ouml;mek edip, olar
a&yacute;ryl&yacute;ar we garyn bo&#351;lugy arassalan&yacute;ar.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le
hem hirurgiki interwensi&yacute;a garyn bo&#351;lugynda - peritonitde
&ccedil;i&#351;megi&#328; &yacute;a&yacute;ramagyny&#328; alamatlary
&uuml;&ccedil;in ulanyl&yacute;ar.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;t haltasynda
&yacute;a-da &ouml;t haltasynda da&#351;lar bar bolsa, a&#351;gazan asty
m&auml;zini&#328; &ccedil;ykmagyna mehaniki ta&yacute;dan p&auml;sgel
ber&yacute;&auml;n &ccedil;i&#351;ler, degi&#351;li hirurgiki
&ccedil;&auml;reler ge&ccedil;iril&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Durmu&#351;y&#328;
hilini dikeltmek we gowula&#351;dyrmak</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:
13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>D&uuml;zg&uuml;n
bol&#351;y &yacute;aly, &ouml;d &yacute;a-da alkogolly pankreatiti&#328;
&yacute;um&#351;ak g&ouml;rn&uuml;&#351;ine e&yacute;e bolan
n&auml;saglary&#328; durmu&#351; derejesi
peselme&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;Alamatlar azalanda hassalar adaty
i&yacute;mitleni&#351;e we i&#351;je&#328;lige &yacute;uwa&#351;lyk bilen
ga&yacute;d&yacute;arlar.&nbsp;A&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; k&ouml;p
nekrozy bilen ferment &yacute;etmez&ccedil;iligi, &#351;e&yacute;le hem
s&uuml;&yacute;ji keseli &ouml;s&uuml;p biler.&nbsp;&#350;e&yacute;le
&#351;ertler yzygiderli bejergini we lukman&ccedil;ylyk
g&ouml;zeg&ccedil;iligini talap ed&yacute;&auml;r.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:18.0pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>M&uuml;mkin
kyn&ccedil;ylyklar</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Ulgamla&yacute;yn &ccedil;i&#351;me sindromy we k&ouml;p
agzany&#328; n&auml;sazlygy sindromy,&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&#351;gazan
asty fermentlerini&#328; gana k&ouml;p mukdarda &ccedil;ykmagy, serho&#351;
bolmagy we i&ccedil;ki organlara zeper &yacute;etmegi fonunda
&ouml;s&yacute;&auml;r.&nbsp;</span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:
"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Aciti pankreatiti&#328; irki
d&ouml;w&uuml;rlerinde &ouml;l&uuml;mi&#328; esasy seb&auml;bi &#351;u.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>A&#351;gazan&nbsp;</span></b><span style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>asty m&auml;zini&#328;&nbsp;<b>psevdosy&nbsp;</b>-
&yacute;akyn organlary&#328; diwarlary bilen &ccedil;&auml;klendirilen
a&#351;gazan asty m&auml;zini&#328; &#351;iresi.&nbsp;</span><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>Diwary&#328;
&yacute;arylmagy we gan akmagy, &yacute;oka&#351;ma howpy bilen bilelikde
bol&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Absess we flegmon&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>garyn
bo&#351;lugynda yiringli &ccedil;i&#351;meleri&#328; merkezidir.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Garyn bo&#351;lugyna &yacute;a-da a&#351;gazan-i&ccedil;ege
ulgamyna gan akma, a&#351;gazan&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US
style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>asty
m&auml;zini&#328; &#351;iresi bilen damar diwarlaryna zeper &yacute;etmegi
&yacute;a-da yiringli amallar wagtynda &yacute;&uuml;ze
&ccedil;yk&yacute;ar.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Peritonit&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>, &#351;ol sanda yiringli,
peritony&#328; &yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy &yacute;oka&#351;mazdan &yacute;a-da
&yacute;oka&#351;magydyr.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Sepsis, septiki zarba we k&ouml;p agzany&#328;
n&auml;sazlygy&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>- gan akmasy bilen
&yacute;okan&ccedil;lygy&#328; &auml;hli organlara we dokumalara
&yacute;a&yacute;ramagy.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:
Symbol;color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Fistulalar&nbsp;</span></b><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>a&#351;gazan asty&nbsp;<b>m&auml;zinden&nbsp;</b>,
meselem, on iki barmakly i&ccedil;ege gir&yacute;&auml;n patologiki
ge&ccedil;i&#351;lerdir.&nbsp;Wagty&#328; ge&ccedil;megi bilen &ouml;zleri
&yacute;ap&yacute;arlar, &yacute;a-da hirurgiki bejergi zerur bolup
biler.&nbsp;</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:
14.0pt;margin-left:0in;line-height:normal'><b><span style='font-size:18.0pt;
font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;color:black'>&Ouml;&#328;&uuml;ni aly&#351;
&ccedil;&auml;releri</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
color:black'>·<span style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>&Ouml;t da&#351; keselini we onu&#328; kyn&ccedil;ylyklaryny
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly bejermek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>Alkogol i&ccedil;gilerinden ga&ccedil;a durmak.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>I&yacute;mit - ajy, &yacute;agly, kakadylan i&yacute;mitleri
a&#351;a k&ouml;p sarp etmek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:-.25in;line-height:
normal'><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;color:black'>·<span
style='font:7.0pt "Book Antiqua"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span lang=EN-US style='font-size:13.5pt;font-family:"Book Antiqua",serif;
color:black'>On iki barmakly i&ccedil;ege &yacute;arasyny
&ccedil;yl&#351;yrymly bejermek.</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:14.0pt;margin-left:64.9pt;text-indent:
-.25in;line-height:normal'><span style='font-size:10.0pt;font-family:Symbol;
